# sendMail (code_share/views):
 - used heroku plugin called trustfi
 - https://elements.heroku.com/addons/categories/email-sms
 - according to https://api.trustifi.com/ we can send mail with curl code
 - using : https://reqbin.com/req/python/c-xgafmluu/convert-curl-to-python-requests, we converted curl to python code to send the mail
 - to get keys:
     goto https://dashboard.heroku.com/apps/ioee/resources
     click trustifi
     top right corner dropdown
     settings
     at the bottom you can get keys you need

# escape in python format '{{}}'
'{\'hello\'} {name}'.format(name=name) #err.
'{{\'hello\'}} {name}'.format(name=name) #err.